text.tspan: Average shower length is 8 minutes, with water flowing at 3.5 gallons per minute
Average person uses the restroom 6 times a day with 2 gallons per flush
HYGIENE (Washing hands, washing face, brushing teeth, etc.)
Average flow rate of a bathroom faucet is 1.5 gallons per minute
FOOD AND DRINK (Cooking, washing dishes, and drinking water)
Average flow rate of a kitchen faucet is 2 gallons per minute
